@node Main "LineBloks - Documentation"

                            'LineBloks' 1.01

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'LineBloks' is @{" played " link play} on an 8 by 8 tile board, the idea is to align 8
tiles of the same pattern in a row or column. When a row or column is filled
with the same type of tiles, those tiles are removed from the board.

  As the game progress, in addition to the normal tiles, Bombs, Unclickable
tiles, Lightning tiles and Blocks are added in the game board.

  Have fun!

               @{" Install and Play the game " link play}
               @{"   Features of the game    " link features}
               @{"          History          " link histo}
